summary: Hi! I just wanted to let you know I LOVE your music so much! I couldn't stop listening to "Around Me" and it brought tears to my...
question: Hi! I just wanted to let you know I LOVE your music so much! I couldn't stop listening to "Around Me" and it brought tears to my eyes thinking of Ben & Rey finally finding peace together. I wasn't even a Reylo before TLJ but the last Force bond scene left me feeling so heartbroken for them - and yet hopeful for a happy ending in IX. Your song made me imagine just how beautiful a final scene between them after all the conflict will be. Thank you for that! Keep up the wonderful work.
answer:
Wow! If waking up to kind words like these don’t make your day, I don’t know what will! Thank you so, so, so much. I am incredibly happy that you like our music! It means the world to hear from people who are appreciating it.

Sending you the biggest hug, anon!


For my friends who are new to following me, I am one half of a lady Folk duo called MissThis. Our music is heavily inspired by Star Wars (Reylo in particular). We have put out three songs thus far—StarCrossed, Rumors, and AroundMe.

Listen to ‘AroundMe’ here:
